events.name: Singapore PHP User Group Meetup (Jan 2016)
events.description:
It's time to kick start the new year with a meetup!

Venue: Level 7, Suntec Tower 5.

Speakers:
=======

1) Singapore PHP and developer community stats
Speaker: Sayanee Basu

2) How to refactor your PHP code like a pro
Speaker: Michael Cheng

3) Lightning talks

a) Converting Dynamic Sites to Static
Speaker: Zion Ng, intZone.com

(Open to the floor for 5 minute talks by anyone with an idea to share. Send me your proposal nowat miccheng@phpug.sg)

=================
